{"tid":1745191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"極品藍黑酒樓 介紹返俾大家","createTime":"2019-11-22T05:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T05:55:52.000Z","uid":228814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97bbb403db16841e6f2257a2168fe81baf2c94bc","tid":1745191,"uid":228814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LELr390.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLELr390.png&h=f471f52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日同親戚朋友去咗一間酒樓飲茶，等咗成粒鐘都未有位，於是我老母就去睇下到未。點知原來間嘢暗地裏派曬啲位俾啲垃圾廢老藍屍先。因為咁樣係好唔公平，所以我老母就去伸張正義。點知個老細出到嚟，好撚惡咁話唔做我哋生意，叫我哋走喎。最後仲加多句：個社會就係因為多咗你依班人，所以咁亂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰刻真係著咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}